杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 向粉丝透露新单曲《胡迪尼》(Houdini) 的神秘信息https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-teases-new-single-houdini-with-cryptic-messages-to-fans-3527061?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dua-lipa-teases-新单曲胡迪尼与粉丝的神秘信息Max PilleyTue, 31 Oct 2023 18:16:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3527061 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜阿·利帕" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Instagram 帖子包含一个显示曲目标题的代码</p><p>Dua Lipa 的帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-teases-new-single-houdini-with-cryptic-messages-to-fans-3527061">，向歌迷传达了一些神秘的信息，以调侃新单曲“Houdini”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杜阿·利帕" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dua_lipa_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>在 Instagram 上向粉丝发布了一段神秘的视频信息，预告了一首新单曲《Houdini》。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="33" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/dua-lipa-cover-interview-2020-if-somebody-told-me-not-to-discuss-issues-im-passionate-about-i-wouldnt-listen-2644409"><b>Dua Lipa：“如果有人告诉我不要讨论我热衷的问题怎么办？我不听”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位流行歌手在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzEbDjasSBf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">她的帐户</a>上发布了一段新音乐片段，其中可以听到她唱着“告诉我你需要我的所有方式”。</p><p>在片段的末尾，一系列数字闪现：4 8 9 9 14 15 21。这些数字在翻译成对应的字母后，可以重新排列以形成胡迪尼这个名字。</p><p>今天（10 月 31 日）也是这位著名魔术师和逃脱术士于 1926 年去世的周年纪念日。</p><p>对胡迪尼的抽象提及似乎还在继续，利帕嘴里衔着一条金钥匙项链。在他的行动中，胡迪尼逃跑的方法之一是他的妻子在接吻时将手铐的钥匙递给了他。</p><p>这种意象在流行音乐史上曾有过：1982 年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-bush">凯特·布什 (Kate Bush</a> ) 的专辑《The Dreaming》的封面上描绘了这位歌手嘴里叼着一把钥匙，准备把它交给某人。该专辑还收录了一首名为“Houdini”的曲目。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CzEbDjasSBf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: f